#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimer; is an application that lets you start an application after a "
"certain amount of time has passed."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑odbrojavač</application> je KDE program koje vam omogućava da "
"pokrenete neki program nakon što je prošlo izvesno vreme."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
